  "title": "Chapter II — Lythium Basin",
  "expedition": true,
  "theme": "emberwaste",
  "objective": "Descend the terraced refinery basin — raise two relay pylons to wake the southern Anchor, then reach the gate",
  "time": 660,
  "intro": [
    {
      "title": "The Cinder Works",
      "lines": [
        "The basin never flooded. It burned. The levee broke onto a magma vent.",
        "Now the refinery descends in scorched terraces, each shelf cut by lava runs.",
        "Two relays wake the Anchor below. Keep to the cinder causeways — the rock sears."
      ],
      "art": "basin"
    }
  ],
  "outro": [
    {
      "title": "The Basin Settles",
      "lines": [
        "The second relay hums under a crust of cooling slag. The Anchor answers.",
        "Ash drifts over the terraces, settling on the molten brutes you laid down.",
        "South, past the broken gate, the next quorum waits in the dunes."
      ],
      "art": "basin"
    }
  ],
  "captiveChars": [
    "engineer",
    "volt",
    "seal"
  ],
  "npcs": [
    {
      "id": "saba-marrow",
      "name": "Saba Marrow, Cinder-Hunter",
      "lines": [
        "Hsst. Stay off the bare rock — it sears. Cinder crust is cool enough to run.",
        "See the bruisers? Molten through. Drop one and it leaves a burning slick where it fell.",
        "Pyre-beetles crack open when they die — a patch of fire and a little blast. Don't crowd them.",
        "Chargers wind up, then dash. Sidestep on the plaza, never on a causeway over the lava.",
        "Crystal seams glint all down these terraces. Crack every one. The basin owes you."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "foreman-vael",
      "name": "Foreman Eshe Vael",
      "lines": [
        "Lythium Basin works. Three hundred hands on shift when the vent blew. One night. All of it ash.",
        "The refinery shelves still hold above the lava runs. Fight from the cinder — the rock belongs to the fire now.",
        "Two pylons wake this Anchor. One on the middle floor, one down at the south plaza. A quorum of two.",
        "Take these. The last shards we ever refined. Build something that outlasts the burn.",
        "My crews stacked these stones against the heat. Still holding the line. So am I."
      ],
      "gift": {
        "shards": 6
      }
    }
  ],
